snippet.title: Widget Inc. - Scaling Endgame Factory
snippet.description:
As you reach the final stages of the game the amount of resources required to continue will be astronomical. Before starting work on your rocket you'd do best to weed out any inefficiencies and patch holes in your supply line.

Download the free Widget Inc. demo today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3184110/Widget_Inc/
